---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Augustus Nas">
<style>
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); min-height: 480px; }
  .about-left { border-right: 1px solid var(--rule); padding: 48px 40px; background: var(--ink); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
  .about-initials { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 72px; font-weight: 700; color: white; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .about-name { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; color: white; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .about-role { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .about-tagline { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.7; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); padding-top: 24px; }
  .about-right { padding: 48px; }
  .about-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .about-headline { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .about-body { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .credentials { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--rule); margin-top: 32px; }
  .cred-cell { background: var(--paper); padding: 20px; }
  .cred-label { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .cred-value { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .about-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); padding: 36px 20px; }
    .about-initials { font-size: 52px; }
    .about-right { padding: 32px 20px; }
    .credentials { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>

<div class="about-grid">
  <div class="about-left">
    <div>
      <div class="about-initials">AN</div>
      <div class="about-name">Augustus Nas</div>
      <div class="about-role">Transformation & Diagnostic Advisory</div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-tagline">Based in London. Working with founders and leadership teams across the UK and Europe.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-right">
    <div class="about-eyebrow">About me</div>
    <h1 class="about-headline">Most organisations I work with already know something is wrong.</h1>
    <p class="about-body">They can feel it — in the meetings that circle the same problems, the strategies that get announced but not adopted, the capable people who have stopped contributing fully. The diagnosis is usually not hard. What is hard is saying it clearly, to the right people, in a way that doesn't trigger the defensive manoeuvres that killed the last three attempts at change.</p>
    <p class="about-body">My work begins with that diagnosis. Not with a framework, not with a programme, but with the question of what is actually happening here — and why it keeps happening.</p>
    <p class="about-body">In practice, that means understanding how decisions actually get made, how performance is actually measured, and what the incentive structures actually reward. It means distinguishing between the stated strategy and the operating reality. Those two things are rarely the same.</p>
    <p class="about-body">I have worked across public sector transformation, financial services, and technology — in organisations ranging from early-stage companies to government departments. The specifics differ; the structural problems tend not to.</p>
    <p class="about-body">I work with a small number of engagements at any one time. That is by design. The work requires depth, not coverage.</p>
    <p class="about-body">Most of what gets called transformation is really reorganisation. Moving the boxes, renaming the roles, commissioning the strategy document. The underlying conditions that produced the problem remain untouched. I am interested in the conditions.</p>
    <p class="about-body">If your organisation is facing a transformation that has stalled, a strategy that is not landing, or a leadership team pulling in different directions — I am worth a conversation.</p>
    <div class="credentials">
      <div class="cred-cell">
        <div class="cred-label">Domain</div>
        <div class="cred-value">Transformation & Diagnostic Advisory</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cred-cell">
        <div class="cred-label">Geography</div>
        <div class="cred-value">UK & Europe</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cred-cell">
        <div class="cred-label">Engagement</div>
        <div class="cred-value">Project-based & Retained</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>